Variables
---------
md	mode number
md$	mode description
pr	rgb palette for mode
pc	cmp palette for mode
pl	palette number
mn$	monitor type (rgb or cmp)
ct	category
ct$	category description
vd	video to play
sv	start of video list for filtering
ev	last video filtered
nv	number of videos filtered in current list (max 8)
vf$()	array of filtered video names
vf()	matching list of video record numbers

Subsections
-----------
frame		1000
main menu	1100
setup menu	1200
monitor	menu	1300
video mode menu	1400
palette mapping	1600
video category	1700
video select	1900
video filter	2200
play video	2400

Sample modes file
-----------------
"128X192-16",0,1
"128X96-16",0,1
"128X96-256",-1,2
"128X192-2",3,4
"256X192-2",3,4
"128X96-4 GYBR",5,6
"128X96-4 BCMO",7,8
"128X192-4 BWRB",9,10

